  "original_title": "\u0d8b\u0dc3\u0dc3\u0dca\u0db4\u0dd9\u0dc5 \u0dc4\u0db4\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "High school is here",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ishara Lakmal Heenkenda, who studied at Badulla Candagolla Maha Vidyalaya, managed to record the most outstanding result among the students who secured the top positions in the island in the 2021 General Certificate of Advanced Level Examination. Recorded the first place in the island in the art section.",
        "Neranda Dilhara Kumarasinghe student of Naramla Mayurapara Central High School has won the first place in the engineering technology section.",
        "Tamilvanan Tuvarakesh, student of St. Michael's College, Batticaloa, stood first in the biology section.",
        "Ishini Neha Amararatne, a student of Gampaha Ratnawali Girls' College, managed to get the first place in the island in the commercial section."
      ],
